SELECT Host_city_ID, Area_km_2 FROM farm_competition INNER JOIN city ON farm_competition.Host_city_ID = city.City_ID WHERE Status IN(SELECT Status FROM city WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM farm_competition WHERE Competition_ID <> (SELECT MIN(Competition_ID) FROM competition_record WHERE Competition_ID IN(SELECT Competition_ID FROM competition_record AS o WHERE  o.Rank > ((() / ()) + SQRT(o.Competition_ID)) / 66) LIMIT 5 OFFSET 2) AND city.City_ID = Host_city_ID)) GROUP BY Area_km_2 HAVING MAX(Year) <= 51 ORDER BY Host_city_ID ASC LIMIT 10 OFFSET 6
